OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FSouthampton players may have a case to
OL,8,Fterminate their contracts and walk
OL,9,Faway for free this summer, the EFL's
OL,10,Fformer head of legal has said.
OL,12,FThe club have been expelled from the
OL,13,FChampionship play-offs after admitting
OL,14,Fthree counts of spying on opposition
OL,15,Ftraining sessions this campaign and
OL,16,Fhave also been docked four points for
OL,17,Fnext season.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
