PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FThe sanction denies the club a shot at
OL,8,Fa place in the Premier League in
OL,9,FSaturday's play-off final worth an
OL,10,Festimated #200million as a minimum `
OL,11,Fand players could argue they have lost
OL,12,Fthat opportunity to play at a higher
OL,13,Flevel and earn a higher salary due to
OL,14,Frule breaches by the club.
OL,16,FFIFA regulations do permit a player to
OL,17,Funilaterally terminate a contract when
OL,18,Fthere is just cause.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FGeoff Cunningham, a former legal chief
OL,8,Fat the EFL and now the sports partner
OL,9,Fat national law firm Clarion, said:
OL,10,F"Fundamentally, the club has acted in
OL,11,Fbad faith and breached the regulations
OL,12,Fof the league and in doing so, have
OL,13,Faffected the players' chances of
OL,14,Fearning their maximum remuneration
OL,15,Fpackages out of their contract, so on
OL,16,Fthe face of it, there is a form of
OL,17,Fbreach of contract.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,F"One thing I imagine Southampton needs
OL,8,Fto be very careful of, and protect
OL,9,Fheavily against and defend heavily, is
OL,10,Fany notion that that potential breach
OL,11,Fof contract is severe enough to enable
OL,12,Fthat player to terminate their
OL,13,Fcontract, then making them a free
OL,14,Fagent to disappear into the summer
OL,15,Fwindow."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
