PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FCunningham said the sanction did seem
OL,8,F"incredibly harsh" on the face of it,
OL,9,Fbut believes the true extent of what
OL,10,FSouthampton have admitted to will only
OL,11,Fbecome clear once the written reasons
OL,12,Fbehind the independent commission's
OL,13,Fdecision are published.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
