PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,FHe said the high stakes of the play-
OL,8,Foffs were clearly "relevant" for the
OL,9,Fcommission to consider when deciding a
OL,10,Fsanction, and added: "I think it's
OL,11,Fmore to do with the deliberate,
OL,12,Fmalicious attempt, in a clandestine
OL,13,Fway, to snoop on another club's
OL,14,Ftraining session ` that is just
OL,15,Fintolerable behaviour.
OL,17,F"If you're on that panel, you have to
OL,18,Fstep back and look at the intention,
OL,19,Fand the intention is not good.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@\O]rD@VOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,F"The intention is to deliberately find
OL,8,Fa way, knowingly, to breach the
OL,9,Fregulations to find even a small
OL,10,Fpercentage or advantage to beat your
OL,11,Fopponent."
OL,13,FCunningham said the EFL deserved major
OL,14,Fcredit for expediting the proceedings,
OL,15,Fwith charges only laid on May 8.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,F"The league should be acknowledged in
OL,8,Fhow quickly this issue has been
OL,9,Fbrought to a hearing and how quickly
OL,10,Fthe outcome has been provided. Whether
OL,11,Fpeople agree with the outcome or not
OL,12,Fis a separate matter," he said.
OL,14,F"They have quickly investigated,
OL,15,Fthey've charged and got it into a
OL,16,Fhearing, had an appeal, all before a
OL,17,Fplay-off final.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@VO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1779440815
OL,3,CSouthampton players may have case to
OL,4,Cterminate contracts, says former EFL
OL,5,Clawyer
OL,7,F"It's incredible that they've gone to
OL,8,Fthose efforts to achieve that, and
OL,9,Fthat's not without a lot of hard work
OL,10,Ffrom their legal team.
OL,12,F"The league has performed
OL,13,Ffantastically for its competition and
OL,14,Fdone a great job. It has no ability to
OL,15,Faffect the outcome, other than to seek
OL,16,Fa sanction from the disciplinary
OL,17,Fcommission."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@LO]
